videos.description: After scoring their first basket against Villanova, La Salle fans honor the Philadelphia Big 5 tradition by throwing streamers onto the court. A technical foul was assessed, but the Wildcats decline to take the free throw.
videos.headline: La Salle fans throw streamers after first bucket against Villanova
La Salle gets the and-one dunk after forcing a turnover
Jordan Price spins through traffic on his way to a lay-up
Villanova steal leads to a lay-up in transition
La Salle lay-up beats the buzzer to cut Villanova lead to 4 heading into halftime

videos.description: Jalen Brunson feeds Donte DiVincenzo for the alley-oop jam in Villanova's win over La Salle.
videos.headline: DiVincenzo throws down an alley-oop to extend Villanova's lead

videos.headline: La Salle 2-handed dunk cuts into the Villanova lead

videos.headline: DiVincenzo dunk seals win for Villanova

videos.description: Mike Couzens and Doris Burke break down Villanova's win over La Salle.
videos.headline: Brunson key in Villanova's win over La Salle

videos.description: Jalen Brunson scores 26 points as No. 1 Villanova improves to 9-0 with an 89-79 victory over La Salle.
videos.headline: No. 1 Villanova tops La Salle to remain undefeated
